Share what you are currently listening to on YTMusic, to your Discord friends! 
____________________________________________________________________________
IMPORTANT
^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Don't minimize the browser window with discord running, else the extension won't work.
The discord tab must be the one selected on the browser window for it to work and the extension will switch the tab automatically before updating your status.
You can cover the browser window with discord with other apps, or move it to another workspace.
